{
  "chapter": "014",
  "title": "十二诸侯年表",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "读春秋而叹",
      "text": ""
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "读谱至厉王",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>阅读<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">春秋</span>历谱谱牒，读到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周厉王</span>时，未尝不放下书来叹息。"
    },
    "1.2": {
      "title": "师挚见微",
      "text": "说：唉，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">师挚</span>是看到这种苗头的啊！"
    },
    "1.3": {
      "title": "象箸之叹",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>制作<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">象箸</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">箕子</span>就为之叹惜。"
    },
    "1.4": {
      "title": "关雎作",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>道衰缺，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">诗</span>人就从夫妇衽席之事写起，于是<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">关雎</span>之诗产生了。"
    },
    "1.5": {
      "title": "鹿鸣刺",
      "text": "<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁义</span>衰微，<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">鹿鸣</span>之诗就来讽刺。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "共和行政之始",
      "text": ""
    },
    "2.1": {
      "title": "厉王奔彘",
      "text": "到了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周厉王\">厉王（周厉王）</span>时，他讨厌听到别人指出他的过错，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span>们害怕被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>而祸乱发作，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周厉王\">厉王（周厉王）</span>于是逃奔到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彘</span>地，祸乱从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京师</span>开始，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">共和</span>之治也由此开始。"
    },
    "2.2": {
      "title": "强凌弱",
      "text": "此后有的诸侯凭武力专政，强凌弱，兴兵不请命于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。"
    },
    "2.3": {
      "title": "五伯擅政",
      "text": "然而他们还打着王室的旗号，以讨伐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>而成为会盟的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">盟主</span>，政令由<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五伯</span>发出，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>肆意妄为，奢侈不法，篡弑的乱臣贼子纷纷出现。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "四国称伯",
      "text": ""
    },
    "3.1": {
      "title": "初封甚微",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>四国在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">成周</span>时都很弱小，所封之地有的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百里</span>，有的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五十里</span>。"
    },
    "3.2": {
      "title": "四海迭兴",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国凭借<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三河</span>之险，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国背靠<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东海</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国介于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江淮</span>之间，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国凭借<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍州</span>的险固，四海之中交替兴起，轮流做伯主，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文武</span>所褒奖的大封国，都靠威力使他们臣服。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "孔子作春秋",
      "text": ""
    },
    "4.1": {
      "title": "干七十余君",
      "text": "所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>阐明<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">王道</span>，干谒过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十馀君</span>，没有人能任用他，于是西行观察<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>室，研讨<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">史记</span>旧闻，从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国开始编次<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">春秋</span>，上自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁隐公\">隐（鲁隐公）</span>，下至<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁哀公\">哀（鲁哀公）</span>获麟，简约其辞文，去其繁重，以此制定义法，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">王道</span>完备，人事周洽。"
    },
    "4.2": {
      "title": "七十子口传",
      "text": "<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十子</span>之徒以口相传其要旨，因为有讥讽褒讳挹损的文辞，不可在书上显露出来。"
    },
    "4.3": {
      "title": "左丘明作左氏春秋",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">左丘明</span>担心弟子们各持异端，各自依附自己的见解，失去原意，所以依据<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">史记</span>详尽地叙述这些话，写成<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">左氏春秋</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "后世诸家春秋",
      "text": ""
    },
    "5.1": {
      "title": "铎氏微",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">铎椒</span>给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚威王</span>做师傅，因为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>不能通读<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">春秋</span>，他就采择其中成败的事例，共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十章</span>，写成<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">铎氏微</span>。"
    },
    "5.2": {
      "title": "虞氏春秋",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵孝成王</span>时，他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">虞卿</span>上采<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">春秋</span>，下观近世形势，也著述<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八篇</span>，成为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">虞氏春秋</span>。"
    },
    "5.3": {
      "title": "吕氏春秋",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦庄襄王</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，也上观古代，删取<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">春秋</span>，汇集<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六国</span>时事，写成<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">八览</span>、<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六论</span>、<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">十二纪</span>，成为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">吕氏春秋</span>。"
    },
    "5.4": {
      "title": "诸子捃摭",
      "text": "至于像<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荀卿</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟子</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙固</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩非</span>一辈人，也各自往往撷取<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">春秋</span>的文辞而著书，多得难以尽数。"
    },
    "5.5": {
      "title": "张苍董仲舒",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>推算<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">五德</span>的历谱，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">董仲舒</span>推演<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">春秋</span>的义理，也颇有著述。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "作年表缘由",
      "text": ""
    },
    "6.1": {
      "title": "诸家不合",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">儒者</span>断取其义理，游说之士夸饰其辞令，都不致力于综括其始终；治历法的人只取其年月，数术家推崇神运之说，谱谍只记世系谥号，文辞简略，想要一览其要旨很难。"
    },
    "6.2": {
      "title": "作十二诸侯表",
      "text": "于是编排十二<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的谱系，自<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">共和</span>至<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>，表列<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">春秋</span>、<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">国语</span>中<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">学者</span>所讥评的盛衰大旨，著于本篇，为有志于精通古文的人作为要删。"
    }
  }
}